description:
She's a sassy bookstore manager, he's a famous actor. This Notting
Hill-inspired New Adult romance is outrageous, funny, and full of
sex, sex, sex. Peaches Monroe, age 22, is a plus-sized beauty who
spends quiet days with books, in the small town of Beaverdale,
Washington. One Saturday afternoon, she's balancing precariously
on a chair, in a bridesmaid dress, when a handsome dark-haired man
comes running into the bookstore. He knocks Peaches over, she lands
in his muscular arms. 

We Are Made Of Stardust (Peaches Monroe #1)
